    <title>五一，趁兴而行</title>
    <url>/2021/05/09/%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%B6%81%E5%85%B4%E8%80%8C%E8%A1%8C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>04-16和同事就规划好行程，五一黄山五人行 </p>
<h3 id="Day-1"><a href="#Day-1" class="headerlink" title="Day 1"></a>Day 1</h3><p>我们成功的低估了疫情后的第一个五一人流量，师徒四人在高铁上站了两个小时后抵达黄山。<br>还有一个人门钥匙拔不出来了，晚上11点才成功会师。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSMW5BNGkzVXZOVHdlTWlaeXFrWFFKTkVHb3RkZ3U1Ri93PT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>小巷中的民宿，特意推到墙，种上了爬墙虎，超级nice。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSeU5sZ05pM0lXc0ZqOWJTdXdHMzlYd0lvQXRiVCtlbmpBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>三人剪影，夸夸我的摄影技术，hhhhhhhhhh。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSMEdISlFTUHA0Tk5SNUNHT3NjNk1xZjlYUjVhMTlyZ2xRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"><br><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSeDczem9aMnQ2UThjcG16U2xCano5TmhDQ243ZDFOK3ZnPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>伴着落日余晖，夜泊屯溪。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSODNQZnY5ZVJSOGJ6Z2NDOWlRWmN1YnBZczk0RWVuUEVRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>开启剧本杀之夜，等到同伴会师后，我们才入眠。</p>
<h3 id="Day-2"><a href="#Day-2" class="headerlink" title="Day 2"></a>Day 2</h3><p>古老的建筑群（不知道是不是重建的），很适合拍人像，hhhh。<br>有人像照，我不放，欸，就是玩！</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNlFCZytxMEpYZ1E0QlNrY2U3NVV0ZXYrdndxQi90WnVBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>熙熙攘攘（稀稀疏疏）的路口</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf3.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSOGFLYTBlUGlWQlhpL0JjVEY3bGw5dTU1VmtvbTIyYVhRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>卡夫卡，错了。卡旺卡奶茶店门口的风铃成功引起我的注意，差点就把它从老板娘手里收走了。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNUZ3c1ljQkJ4VExjb3dIMDN4MzBVdWNieVhCRUJoM2d3PT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<h3 id="Day-3"><a href="#Day-3" class="headerlink" title="Day 3"></a>Day 3</h3><p>3号一早，我们就出发，转车前往宏村。  </p>
<p>经过两天的徒步游览，耗尽了我们的精力，在宏村顶着烈日游览一个小时后，达到回宾馆，玩了一下午的剧本杀（深度沉迷）。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNXNzcGRDS3BHSjRub0RIbGZvODNneTM0b3c1SUlYTVZnPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p><img src="https://imglf3.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNG5Gam5qcFVKbjNubGgxcDBUNEU2UnhyRmxGTlJxcjBBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>Day 3 end</p>
<h3 id="Day-4"><a href="#Day-4" class="headerlink" title="Day 4"></a>Day 4</h3><p>第二天一早，买完烧饼后，买包子的工夫，被一位大哥捞上了他的顺风车。  </p>
<p>避开了等大巴的时间，9点过我们就到达黄山脚下。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSeWd6ZVVnVW16SVdyaWx6M0JyOWpnMFpkWHQvcEdRaGlRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>云雾环绕的山峰，那是我们最终的目的地。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSMWpCRXlIeFVrUzZ6b1o2OGdZeGZTTWVUV2dVL0ZKaDlnPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>走进灰蒙蒙的深山之中。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSN3pNdkNuUGhPcFBpS3gra3hVNVBFK3BETmEzbmhDckVBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>浮云不共此山齐，山霭苍苍望转迷。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSM2xzZTM0blFmenZIaTRJQnpST1p5cHkzMVhRSzU5ejJRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>山中柴门。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNVRlbm1YTmFNRk5zZVM2YUVqeWhlQjBxQUxHZ2dVQUpBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>还有很多超级可爱的小松鼠，刚好被我拍到一只。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSNDVGOTlUTElaUUh0S3o2LzFia1pxMXJQSFlSOGIyeEhRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>路上捡到小松鼠的零食（松果）</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSL013SjE3dDFOVWt1bGUyeEhDbm1rUnR3bE10NFBSQTZRPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>黄山第二高峰——光明顶。有一个气象观测站，但是没有办法进去。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSOTMxdHhrQzcvL2lXUElwc0dQdHhKMkp5WE5QVkppWEl3PT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>勇者，都会攀登一线天，只能上，不能下（从另一条路下）。</p>
<p><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/RC9SYWg2TlFGakN3ZWJQVzM5M3hSMnhEb1JTSkRrK0xQeCtjQkw0WGhBeFBsRGo4cEk3dnhBPT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage"></p>
<p>从第一高峰莲花峰下来的路上（伙伴说这边很险，不敢下，我独自一人从这边走下莲花峰）</p>
]]></content>
