    <title>十一，哑巴之旅</title>
    <url>/2021/10/07/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%93%91%E5%B7%B4%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>早早和同事说好十一时去舟山看海，但是！他们9月突然变卦，都想回家，因此好好的四人行变成了我一个人的哑巴之旅。  </p>
<p>高铁上的长江大桥，说实话，作为一个四川人，真的是第一次看到这么多的船（电视上除外）<br><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/71c5b258765398d0/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwTGlOb3g3amg4YUkxMExSNithbi9CWT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>在小镇中穿流而过，一簇在水中绽放。<br><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/5706ef85262018f2/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwRjkrTlVpdjFVQmROcmZocUlZM3M3Zz0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>载有游客的小船摇摇晃晃。<br><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/c2b57eee04b9dd03/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwREtJcDlXc3FHQXpDenhveWZrL3N5az0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>随着夜色降临，天气转凉，河中的小船多了起来。<br><img src="https://imglf3.lf127.net/img/39ac23a51a316d38/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwR1phZHo1THBKa3Y4UnNIcWwvTjBkST0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>镇中有家小吃街，肉食丰富。<br><img src="https://imglf5.lf127.net/img/7f054418e4fa1c1d/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwR0hWNUNNdUhGZytYQ2ZKK1c2blNjOD0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>酸辣的无骨鸡爪填饱了我的肚子。<br><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/105d04bf6fe48082/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwQnlrblFIU0t4ZnRnYXV2Z0Z4bWNtaz0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>夜色中的小桥，让人流连。<br><img src="https://imglf4.lf127.net/img/ec94ca783a69c92c/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwTUQ5OTlqYWpvVER2SFFyWGF3Z1M2WT0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>江南的烟柳繁华，让人痴迷。<br><img src="https://imglf6.lf127.net/img/67c73a73270c0adf/RC9SYWg2TlFGakQ5bkpXRmhlSTVwSzJUU0lSOWFia2xxMkdYMHdqYUp5cz0.jpg?imageView&thumbnail=500x0&quality=96&stripmeta=0&type=jpg" alt="thisisimage">  </p>
<p>到了江南，真正的体会到了富裕之地的繁华生活。小贩的吆喝，人们的吵闹，让这个生活在现代城市的古代小镇活了起来。<br>江南好，风景旧曾……</p>
]]></content>
